    "title": "Durian Furniture is Hiring: Floor Manager (Entry-Level)",
    "description": "We at Durian Furniture are looking for an experienced Floor Manager based out of Ludhiana. If you are a result-oriented professional with a passion for excellence, we want to hear from you.\n\nAbout Durian Furniture:\nDurian Furniture is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Conduct regular stock audits and prevent pilferage\n• Train and motivate the sales team to deliver excellent service\n• Handle customer queries, complaints, and escalations effectively\n• Ensure compliance with company policies and retail regulations\n• Build relationships with regular customers to drive loyalty\n• Prepare daily sales reports and share insights with management\n• Maintain high standards of store hygiene and cleanliness\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Tech / B.E. in Computer Science or related discipline\n• 0-1 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Customer Service\n• Proficiency in SAP Retail\n• Proficiency in Omnichannel Retail\n• Proficiency in MS Excel\n• Proficiency in Supply Chain\n• Proficiency in KPI Management\n• Proficiency in Team Leadership\n• Proficiency in Planogram\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Learning & development budget\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Salary Range: 2.5 LPA - 6 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Ludhiana, Punjab, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Durian Furniture!",
